How I resolved in AS...

- Full reinstall. No change.
- Removed all plugins.  
- Restarted
- Error "missing essential plugin org.jetbrains.android"
- Deleted C:\Users\YourUserName\AppData\Roaming\Google\AndroidStudioPreview4.1\disabled_plugins.txt
- Restarted
- Reapplied plugins flutter dart (kotlin) 
- Restarted
